Product_Title: Seven Days of Birthday Treats Advent Box - contains £59 worth of products
Body_Html:
Why limit your birthday celebrations to just on the day itself, when you could have a whole birthday week?!

Introducing our new Sevens Days of Birthday Treats Advent Box , designed to help you count down to your birthday in style!

♥︎ Each item will be individually wrapped in stunning birthday-themed packaging.  They will also be numbered so you can countdown from Seven days before to the Big day!

♥︎ The products included will change regularly to keep the surprises coming, & the entire contents will change every year, so you don't have to worry about doubling up if you'd like a birthday countdown next year too!

♥︎ You can order up to a year in advance so if your birthday is months away we'll deliver just in time to count down to your birthday and you might forget you ordered it too.

Important Information - Delivery

♥︎ Please specify a dispatch date in the notes at checkout 

♥︎ We recommend selecting a date at least 2 weeks prior to the recipient's birthday to ensure timely delivery. If no date is provided, the order will be sent immediately and we cannot be held responsible for early arrival.

♥︎ For delivery times see the pink banner bar at the top of our website on our home page.  

Is this for a gift?

♥︎ If you would like to gift this to a loved one, add your special gift message in the notes section at checkout and we will handwrite it onto a Birthday notecard, then just add their shipping details and we will send it directly to them!

What's in the Box?

♥︎ If you like what is on our website that will give you a good indication of what might be in the box style wise.

♥︎ Each gift will be something for you or something for your home.

♥︎ Non of the box contents are available to buy on our website, so you can rest assured there is no risk of any product duplication.

♥︎ I can confirm that there will be no scented products in there, such as creams, and no alcohol.

♥︎ I can also let you know that the RRP of the contents is significantly higher than the cost of the box.

Please Note

♥︎ Our Seven Days of Birthday Treats Advent Box is prepared in advance and We are unable to accept any special requests.

Images are for illustrative purposes only.  I want to keep the contents as a surprise!

Product_Title: Here For You Always Rustic Heart Token
Body_Html:
Send a heart-warming message of love and friendship with this rustic pebble token.

Fashioned into a tactile heart shaped pebble, this small token of love reads the words ‘Here for you always’ in a classic font almost pressed into the stone. This sentimental shiny grey heart pebble will give reassurance and positive motivation to your cherished friend when they hold this in their hand.

This Heart Token would make a special friend or family member know that they are truly in your thoughts, a touching gift for your loved one!

Product_Title: Owl Always Love You Owl - Matchbox Gift
Body_Html:
This cute little Owl ornament is perfect for celebrating a love for the adorable animals and will look brilliant displayed in any room of your home!

Made from cream ceramic with a smooth finish, the owl is stood facing forward.  The only added details are two eyes which have been painted on in black, giving the piece a contemporary, simple and stylish look.

It is presented in a beige coloured matchbox which is decorated with a cursive border surrounding the phrase, ‘Owl always love you’, in a typewriter like font with a little heart illustrated at the bottom. The perfect gift to show your love, this sentimental little ornament makes a wonderful birthday, Christmas or Mother’s Day gift.

Size: 4.5 x 3.2 x 2cm

Product_Title: I Can't Say I Love You Enough Coaster
Body_Html:
This lightly ribbed white porcelain heart-shaped coaster is an excellent gift or decoration for anywhere around the home. Place on your coffee table, dining table or bedside table to hold your favourite drinks and display the sweet message in your home.

The front of the design features a leaping hare at the top with text underneath which reads ‘I can’t say I love you enough so this is a little reminder’. This coaster has a foam pad underneath, so you don’t have to worry about it scratching or marking your favourite furniture!

A brilliant gift to give a loved one or a friend! This item makes a wonderful birthday gift and is sure to be treasured forever.

Reed Diffusers

A fabulous fragrance for your home without the flame.

You will receive a little leaflet with your diffuser to give you tips and advice on how to get the most from it.

size 100ml in a clear glass bottle

 

Jar filled with the highest quality fragrance oils and Eco friendly base.

 

What you will receive

1 x reed diffuser

5 x black reeds

They will be wrapped to protect them in transit, please unwrap them carefully as the bottle is glass.

Fragrances Currently available;

  • Fresh Linen - Light, airy and wonderfully clean, just like freshly washed clothes
  • English Pear & Freesia - features pear which is combined with quince which introduces honey sweetness and is surrounded with white freesia and wild climbing rose. A base of the composition is created of green, fresh and sour nuances of rhubarb along with warm and subtle aromas of patchouli, amber and white musk that stay in a trail.
  • Blueberry & Vanilla - a sweet, mouth-watering blueberry accord with nuances of strawberry, raspberry and blackcurrant on a substantive base of vanilla.
  • Peony & Blush - features peonies in bloom with the bite of red apple and the opulence of jasmine, rose and gillyflower. Mingling with the sensuality of soft, blush suede. Luxurious and seductive. Top note is red apple; middle notes are peony, jasmine, carnation and rose; base note is suede. 
  • Joop-e - Fragrance Oil is similar to the iconic pink aftershave. This classic fragrance conveys a timeless statement of individuality and masculine sensuality. 

DISCLAIMER -Amelia Grace Interiors does not have any links with designer brands, all fragrances are types, they do not contain any sweets, perfume

Matchbox Whale

This adorable little ceramic ornament is perfect for giving to a close friend or family member and will look beautiful displayed in any room of your home.

Made from ceramics with a smooth finish, this piece is beautifully designed and detailed in the shape of a whale complete with patterned engraving which gives this piece a contemporary, simple and stylish look.

It is presented in a beige coloured matchbox which is decorated with a cursive border surrounding the phrase ‘Whaley love you’, in a typewriter like font with a small heart illustrated at the bottom. The perfect gift to show your love for a close friend or family member.

‘Strong Women’ Porcelain Heart Shaped Coaster

This lightly ribbed white porcelain heart-shaped coaster is an excellent gift or decoration for anywhere around your home. Place on your coffee table, dining table or bedside table to hold your favourite drinks and display the message in your home.

The front of the design features black text which reads ‘Strong Women don’t have attitudes they have standards’. This coaster has a foam pad underneath, so you don’t have to worry about it scratching or marking your favourite furniture!

It makes a wonderful gift for that strong lady in your life! a brilliant way to add a small, unique touch to your home and remind you of what’s really important, this item makes a wonderful birthday or new home gift for friends and family to treasure.

‘Lovely Things’ Heart Shaped Coaster

This lightly ribbed white porcelain heart-shaped coaster is an excellent gift or decoration for anywhere around the home. Place on your coffee table, dining table or bedside table to hold your favourite drinks and display the sweet message in your home.

The front of the design features writing which reads ‘Thanks for all the lovely things you do it’s great to have a lovely friend like you’. This coaster has a foam pad underneath, so you don’t have to worry about it scratching or marking your favourite furniture!

A brilliant way to add a small, unique touch to your home and remind you of what’s really important, this item makes a wonderful birthday or new home gift for friends and family to treasure forever.

Autumn Mystery Box

Each box will contain 4 Autumn theme products that’s are not available to purchase separately on the website. So you can be certain that you will not get a duplication of anything else you may purchase from that collection.

Each Autumn box contains the same products so unless you want two of each item I’d recommend to only buy one, or if it’s for a gift.

I love all the products chosen to go in these and I am sure you will love them too ♥︎

As a little thank you the boxes retail for more than the £14.99 together 😊

Body_Html:
A Beautiful Keepsake Coaster For Loved Ones

Heart shaped porcelain coaster with the words 'Those we love don't go away, they walk beside us everyday. Unseen, unheard but always near, still loved, stilled missed and very dear'.

Product_Title: Have you as a mum porcelain coaster
Body_Html:
This lightly ribbed white porcelain heart-shaped coaster is an excellent gift or decoration for anywhere around the home. Place on your coffee table, dining table or bedside table to hold your favourite drinks and display the sweet message in your home.

The front of the design features writing which reads ‘If I didn’t have you as my mum I’d choose you as my best friend’. This coaster has a foam pad underneath, so you don’t have to worry about it scratching or marking your favourite furniture!

A brilliant gift to give your mum for Mother’s Day! This item makes a wonderful birthday gift and is sure to be treasured forever.

Product_Title: Braver than you think porcelain Coaster
Body_Html:
Made from Porcelain, this robust heart-shaped coaster reads "Remember you are braver than you believe stronger than you feel and smarter than you think" with a small hand-drawn heart underneath.

The perfect way to ensure your table and other surfaces remain stain free, this coaster brings a touch of class to your home, and also spreads a message of joy. The base is padded to protect any delicate surface you might wish to place it on.

Product_Title: Matchbox Hedgehog - sending you a hedgehug
Body_Html:
This adorable little animal ornament is perfect for celebrating a love of hedgehogs and will look brilliant displayed in any room of your home!

Made from cream ceramic with a lightly dimpled finish, the cute little hedgehog is sat down in a ball. The only added details are two eyes which have been painted on in black, giving the piece a contemporary, simple and stylish look.

It is presented in a beige coloured matchbox which is decorated with a cursive border surrounding the phrase, ‘Sending you a Hedgehug’, in a typewriter like font. The perfect gift to show your love, this sentimental little ornament makes a wonderful birthday, Christmas or Mother’s Day gift.

This beautiful festive ornament is perfect for adding a little Christmas cheer to any room within your home. Whether it’s hung from a hook on the wall or placed on a dresser or sideboard, its simplistic design and intricate details make it the perfect accessory for the holiday season.

Primarily made from wood featuring a distressed finish, the three figurines of Mary, Joseph and Jesus in his manger stand on top of a pale grey plinth which features a small brown label printed with the words ‘O little town of Bethlehem’. Each character has been individually made with visible signs of carving on each one. Above this and hanging from the wire arch, The Star of Bethlehem peacefully shines over the entire scene. The colour scheme is calming and neutral with tones of grey and beige being at the forefront of the pallet, making it perfect for anywhere in your home.

This would make a lovely gift for anyone who is a fan of the Nativity. Whether it’s for Christmas itself or as a birthday present in preparation for the festive period, its minimalistic design and adorable features are sure to be loved and treasured with it taking pride of place year upon year. 

 Please note this item is handmade and therefore rustic and not perfect.

This elegant yet humorous mug is beautifully produced, with the ribbing from the potter’s wheel apparent in the mug surface. It is cream in colour, with a clear glaze.

A beautiful black line drawn illustration of a kettle and a mug is etched into the centre. The words ‘Stroppy before coffee’ are found next to this illustration along a dot-effect line running through the middle of the piece.

Perfect for enjoying a nice cuppa coffee (and dunking a good biscuit), this mug will look tasteful displayed any table.

Add token of love to the home in the form of this Wobbly Porcelain Mug, a witty and touching gift for a family member or friend who are coffee enthusiasts, on their birthday or at Christmas.

The mug comes beautifully packaged in a presentation gift box.

This elegant mug makes a wonderful gift for any strong woman, with motivational words that are sure to inspire them. It is beautifully produced, with the ribbing from the potter’s wheel apparent in the mug surface. White in colour with a clear glaze, it’s perfect for enjoying a nice cuppa coffee and dunking a good biscuit! 

A beautiful black line drawn illustration is etched around the body of the mug, featuring a potted plant with freshly sprouting leaves beside a watering can. The stirring words ‘Strong Women make waves’ are found next to this illustration in a typographical font.

Presented in a matching gift box, this delightful mug makes a wonderful gift for any daughter, sister, or friend embarking on a new adventure.
